{"tid":399704,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"藍芽耳機Jaybird X3保養代理好高質","createTime":"2017-09-14T07:40:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-14T10:17:37.000Z","uid":53189,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"65374191c388af56898ca87c7004b952e601a4e4","tid":399704,"uid":53189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T07:40:25.000Z","msg":"巴絲們想入手真係諗清楚<br />\n<br />\n我用左兩個月左右個藍芽contact 好似已經有小小問題，可能係個別例啦<br />\n<br />\n咁去保養啦，我屌佢老母間保養代理（Compucon）都on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n打十幾廿次去都唔撚聽電話<br />\n<br />\nFacebook 專門問完隔幾日先覆返佢官方有嘅野<br />\n<br />\n上網寫開星期一至六<br />\n<br />\n星期六上到燈都無開連門口個牌寫都唔係佢公司寫個名嚟<br />\n<br />\n最後我想問有無人試過去保養，係咪直接上去就可以<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a293862591bd086eb6c0770fac173e0ad1c83218","tid":399704,"uid":91594,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T07:50:34.000Z","msg":"直接上去就ok,如果真係壞左會直接換隻新既比你<br />\n之前隻jaybird x2 一年用壞左2隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔會再買jaybird<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n第一隻粗用壞左都算，換左隻新既我錫住黎用，叉電都check哂電壓叉滿就抆唔會長叉，都係幾個月就收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d53e63b05e72fc0bbae9b0b7f809201ce77bc1c","tid":399704,"uid":7758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T07:54:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>直接上去就ok,如果真係壞左會直接換隻新既比你<br />\n之前隻jaybird x2 一年用壞左2隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔會再買jaybird<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n第一隻粗用壞左都算，換左隻新既我錫住黎用，叉電都check哂電壓叉滿就抆唔會長叉，都係幾個月就收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁易壞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n等我仲想用asia miles換隻x3<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"334ccbb69b54f5e59745fba06e03d3a5f766f2cb","tid":399704,"uid"