,上去換左一次好快又壞多次,但已經過左保養<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n再去保養囉，一年內任保<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa423fe22865a7ea59879973758d1735841ea95b","tid":399704,"uid":91594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T08:21:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>第一代粒電打左柴,上去換左一次好快又壞多次,但已經過左保養<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n再去保養囉，一年內任保<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n淨係第一次維修先會直接換新，第二次就擺低比佢整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56d932303a4b57e1f7a57837ee179a6915623b7e","tid":399704,"uid":53189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T08:22:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又上去睇下有無開門啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n頭先上左去啦<br />\n原來係大堂個入去先會見到佢間代理<br />\n我問佢耳機盒上面電話係咪錯<br />\n佢話個個唔係佢地電話嚟...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋佢地星期六都開門"},{"pid":"06889503ae15d275db7e765f7b02e8de25a5b1fa","tid":399704,"uid":53189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T08:24:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>第一代粒電打左柴,上去換左一次好快又壞多次,但已經過左保養<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n再去保養囉，一年內任保<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n淨係第一次維修先會直接換新，第二次就擺低比佢整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n原來係咁㗎...<br />\n但我聽賣耳機個個人講藍芽整唔到多數直接換<br />\n比人水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b3c1af00be0d57a835dbc0e27d6daf65f0a4560","tid":399704,"uid":61675,"like":0,"